# V0.app AI Integration Configuration
# Copy this file and add your V0 API key

# V0.app API Configuration
# Get your API key from https://v0.app/dashboard/api-keys
V0_API_KEY=your_v0_api_key_here

# Note: This will enable V0 as an available model in your AI dashboard
# Users will see "V0 Web Generator (5000/req)" in the model selector
# Each generation will cost 5,000 IDR and be deducted from user balance

# Optional: Customize costs (in lib/services/generate-billing.service.ts)
# Default: 5000 IDR per request
